---
Checks:          '*,-modernize-use-trailing-return-type,-llvm*,-fuchsia*,-altera*,-hicpp*,-cppcoreguidelines-pro-bounds-pointer-arithmetic,-cppcoreguidelines-avoid-do-while,-cppcoreguidelines-avoid-c-arrays,-modernize-avoid-c-arrays,-misc-non-private-member-variables-in-classes'
WarningsAsErrors: ''
